author: Russell Brand
description:
Why is no one asking questions about the attempted assassination of Donald Trump? Russell breaks down the strange anomalies—from the scrubbed digital footprint and lack of press briefings to Joe Rogan and Elon Musk’s take on the mysterious event. With institutional silence and mounting inconsistencies, is the official story falling apart? It’s time to ask: who really benefits from this?
